name: USA Sneaker Bot Collection
description: You will receive scripts that add to cart and go all the way to the final checkout pages for the following sites: Blends, Bodega, Bows and Arrows, Concepts, Extra Butter, Kith, Packer, Politics, Undefeated, and West NYC. You will also receive an add-to-cart only script for Burn Rubber. Videos of scripts in action can be seen here. Requirements: Chrome with the Tampermonkey extension installed. User input required: -Clicking on the item on the New Arrivals page of each website. -Pressing “enter” on the keyboard if a “We do not ship to P. O. Boxes” alert message pops up on the cart page. -Logging into sites that have user accounts and passwords (do this before hand and you should be okay). -Typing your size into the script and maybe having to change a variable or two (it will be documented within the script). Upon purchase you will automatically receive an email with the link to the download.
